                            <p>A classic 1970s dinner party dish that matches elegant French cooking with Russian opulence, Beef Stroganoff is guaranteed to impress. I&#39;ve gone for a cucumber pickle and sauteed potatoes as an accompaniment. For a guide to the history of this aristocratic dish, <a href="http://www.lovefood.com/journal/opinions/14670/retro-classics-beef-stroganoff">click here</a>.</p>


                            <div class="layout">

                                <div class="layout__item u-1/2-lap">

                                    <h3 class="heading heading--delta">Ingredients</h3>

                                    <div class="u-pb- u-pl">
                                        <select id="ingredients-select" class="u-1/1" name="weight-conversion">
